3-12-14/ |access-date=December 14, 2023 |website=[[Reuters]]}}&lt;/ref>{{sfn|Slater|2020|p=226}}&lt;ref name=":222">{{cite web |last=Krauss |first=Joseph |title=Poll finds dramatic rise in Palestinian support for Hamas |url=https://apnews.com/article/hamas-middle-east-science-32095d8e1323fc1cad819c34da08fd87 |publisher=AP News |date=June 15, 2021 |access-date=October 9, 2023}}&lt;/ref>{{sfn|Phillips|2011|p=75}} &lt;!--and for its rejection of Israeli [[Zionism as settler colonialism|settler colonialism]] in Palestine.&lt;ref name=":8" />--> 
